snippet.title: Legend of Mana Gameplay
snippet.description:
Excuse the popping sound. I had a chatroom in the background going off. Very unprofessional of me...
Just me playin some Legend of Mana... I'd keep going but it's too troublesome with how fraps only records 30 seconds for me.
